OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FThe UK risks accelerating the decline
OL,7,Fof the oil and gas industry despite
OL,8,Foverwhelming industry belief that the
OL,9,Fbasin could still have a long-term
OL,10,Ffuture, a report has warned.
OL,12,FThe paper by Aberdeen and Grampian
OL,13,FChamber of Commerce found 93% of the
OL,14,Fbusinesses it surveyed agreed there is
OL,15,Fstill a future for the North Sea if
OL,16,Fthe right economic conditions are
OL,17,Fcreated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FThe 43rd Energy Transition report said
OL,7,Fconfidence in the fossil fuel industry
OL,8,Fis weak due to financial instability,
OL,9,Fplanning delays, transmission charging
OL,10,Fand slow project consenting, rather
OL,11,Fthan a lack of opportunity or
OL,12,Fcapability in the sector.
OL,14,FIt said businesses had repeatedly
OL,15,Fwarned that investment was going
OL,16,Fabroad due to the country's poor
OL,17,Feconomic and regulatory policies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FSome 67% of respondents believed
OL,7,Fplanning decisions about important
OL,8,Fonshore grid infrastructure should be
OL,9,Fmade by the Scottish Government,
OL,10,Frather than local authorities.
OL,12,FAnd 89% support new licences and
OL,13,Fconsents where operators can
OL,14,Fdemonstrate lower emissions than
OL,15,Fimported alternatives and deliver
OL,16,Fgreater UK economic value.
OL,18,FThe report warns of a "growing
OL,19,Ftransition gap", creating
OL,20,Finfrastructure delays and uncertainty
OL,21,Faround government policy.
OL,26,@zD@WOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FIt made a number of recommendations,
OL,7,Fincluding giving consent to the
OL,8,FJackdaw and Rosebank oil fields,
OL,9,Freplacing the Energy Profits Levy with
OL,10,Fan oil and gas price mechanism, and
OL,11,Fquicker planning consent.
OL,13,FAberdeen and Grampian Chamber of
OL,14,FCommerce said the findings showed the
OL,15,Furgent need for a more competitive and
OL,16,Fstable policy environment if the UK is
OL,17,Fto retain the workforce and industrial
OL,18,Fcapability required to deliver both
OL,19,Fenergy security and net zero.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FChief executive Russell Borthwick
OL,7,Fsaid: "For several years now, the
OL,8,Fdominant political narrative has
OL,9,Fincreasingly suggested that the future
OL,10,Fof the North Sea is already decided.
OL,11,FThis report tells a very different
OL,12,Fstory.
OL,14,F"The overwhelming majority of
OL,15,Fbusinesses operating across the energy
OL,16,Fsector still believe there is a future
OL,17,Ffor the basin if the UK creates the
OL,18,Fright fiscal and regulatory conditions
OL,19,Fto support it.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,F"What companies are questioning is not
OL,7,Fthe capability of the North Sea, but
OL,8,Fwhether the UK is still competitive
OL,9,Fenough to attract the investment
OL,10,Frequired to deliver that future."
OL,12,FMr Borthwick said the North Sea
OL,13,Fremained "one of the UK's greatest
OL,14,Findustrial assets" and said the same
OL,15,Fworkforce that built the sector over
OL,16,Fthe last five decades would also be
OL,17,F"critical to delivering offshore wind,
OL,18,Fcarbon capture, electrification and
OL,19,Fwider transition infrastructure".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@aO]uD@JOUvD@RO]yD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FHe said: "But investment follows
OL,7,Fstability, and right now too many
OL,8,Fbusinesses believe the UK is losing
OL,9,Fground to international competitors
OL,10,Foffering clearer policy, faster
OL,11,Fconsenting and more predictable long-
OL,12,Fterm conditions.
OL,14,F"The message from industry is becoming
OL,15,Fincreasingly clear ` you cannot
OL,16,Fdeliver energy security, economic
OL,17,Fgrowth and the energy transition while
OL,18,Fsimultaneously hollowing out the
OL,19,Findustrial base required to achieve
OL,20,Fall three."
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FEnergy Security and Net Zero said:
OL,8,F"Oil and gas production will be with
OL,9,Fus for decades to come, and we will
OL,10,Fmanage existing fields for the
OL,11,Fentirety of their lifespan ` while
OL,12,Factively scaling up clean energy
OL,13,Findustries in the North Sea.
OL,15,F"Our ambitious plans will make the
OL,16,FNorth Sea a clean energy powerhouse
OL,17,Fand support up to 40,000 new jobs in
OL,18,FScotland by 2030."
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779768224
OL,3,COil and gas has long-term future if UK
OL,4,CGovernment backs industry, report says
OL,6,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Decisions on consenting for
OL,8,Foffshore oil and gas projects, as well
OL,9,Fas those on licensing and the
OL,10,Fassociated fiscal regime, are matters
OL,11,Fthat are currently reserved to the UK
OL,12,FGovernment.
OL,14,F"We continue to call on the UK
OL,15,FGovernment to approach decisions for
OL,16,FNorth Sea oil and gas projects on a
OL,17,Frigorously evidence-led, case-by-case
OL,18,Fbasis, with climate compatibility and
OL,19,Fenergy security key considerations."
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
